 drivers/net/ethernet/chelsio/cxgb4/cxgb4.h      |    1 
 drivers/net/ethernet/chelsio/cxgb4/cxgb4_main.c |   97 ++++++++++++++++--------
 2 files changed, 67 insertions(+), 31 deletions(-)

